{
  "block_id": "block_002",
  "segments": [
    {
      "text": "夏辛还没应声，门外就传来一阵动静",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战家老夫人沉着脸走进来，开口问道：彦寒你说什么",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒脚步一顿，喊了声奶奶",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人看着他满身泥泞，头发还挂着枯草",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "气得手里的拐杖都不住地发抖",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "你看看你现在，到底像什么样子",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒一脸淡定，手还在轻轻挠我的头",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人重重吐出一口浊气，骂道：造孽",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒+厌恶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "这只猫就是扫把星，自从进门战家没太平过",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒+厌恶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战家这两年确实流年不利，多灾多难",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "低落",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "二哥三年前坠机，三哥两年半前海难昏迷",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "低落",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "大哥一年前也因车祸不幸身亡",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "低落",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒赶到时，见我遍体鳞伤守在他母亲身边",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "低落",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "从那以后，他就把我养在蓝泽园寸步不离",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "奶奶您把天灾人祸怪在一只猫身上",
      "role": "战彦寒",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.8,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒脸色一沉，语气冰冷地质问",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "就因为这个，您差点打死它吗",
      "role": "战彦寒",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.9,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "你母亲执迷不悟，你也跟着一起疯",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒+低落",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人叹气，命令道：立刻把猫送走",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒+无奈",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒周身戾气暴涨，一字一顿反问",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "我要是不肯呢",
      "role": "战彦寒",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "愤怒+强势",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.9,
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 0.8
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人被噎得说不出话来，面露错愕",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "惊讶+愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒二十二岁接管家族，一年资产翻三倍",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "手段狠厉，连家族长辈都忌惮他三分",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人强压怒火，提出另一个条件",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "不送走也行，那就早点和灵儿完婚",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "压抑的愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人喊道：灵儿！万灵儿乖巧进门",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "万灵儿娇羞低头，轻声唤道：彦寒，灵儿",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "娇羞",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "今天彦寒不去公司，你在蓝泽园陪他",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "命令",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老夫人说完就走，不给战彦寒拒绝机会",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "刺鼻的香水味呛醒了我，我喵呜一声",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "不适+惊吓",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒温柔抚摸我的头，却发现我浑身发抖",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "担忧",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "我拼命往他怀里钻，像刚被捡回来时一样",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "恐惧",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "万灵儿脸色一僵，硬着头皮伸手讨好",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "尴尬",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "西西，来让我抱抱，我会好好疼你的",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "讨好",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "话音刚落，我抖得比刚才更厉害了",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "恐惧",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒眼神幽深，冷冷看向万灵儿",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "冰冷",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "万灵儿干笑，解释道：西西好像怕生",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "尴尬",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒眼睛眯成线，盯得万灵儿心虚低头",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "冰冷",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "突然门外传来一阵骚动，有人闯进来",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "惊讶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "老四听说你猫丢了，动静闹得震动海城",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "活泼",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.2
    },
    {
      "text": "我又给你买了一只，你肯定会喜欢",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "活泼",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.2
    },
    {
      "text": "发小楚逸顶着黄毛，穿荧光粉衬衫哈伦裤",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "风风火火闯进来，怀里还抱着一只白猫",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "平静",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "话没说完，他就看见战彦寒怀里的我",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "惊讶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "我慵懒白他一眼，心里骂：愚蠢的人类",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "傲娇+厌恶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "本尊什么时候丢过，真是多管闲事",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "傲娇+厌恶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "楚逸瞪大眼，惊讶吐槽：这猫什么眼神",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "惊讶+吐槽",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "跟战彦寒一个德行，简直一模一样",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "惊讶+吐槽",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.4,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.2
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒皱眉，冷冷开口：没事你可以走了",
      "role": "战彦寒",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "冰冷",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 0.9
    },
    {
      "text": "我怕你伤心，一大早找了只一模一样的",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "委屈",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.1
    },
    {
      "text": "楚逸气结，提议：把我家这只公的留下",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.4,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.1
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "跟你的配一对，生窝崽子回回血",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "算计",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.1
    },
    {
      "text": "这猫贼贵，我连名字都起好了叫东东",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "emotion": "得意",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0.3,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0,
        0.2
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.1
    },
    {
      "text": "配对！我在他怀里一蹬跳下来炸毛怒吼",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "你瞎吗！那只鸳鸯眼丑成那样配不上本尊",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "愤怒+厌恶",
      "emotion_vector": [
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0.5,
        0,
        0,
        0
      ],
      "speaking_speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "战彦寒看着炸毛的我，嘴角微微勾起",
      "role": "旁白",
      "type": "narration",
      "emotion": "温柔",
      "emotion_vector": [
